<h3 class="bold">Video Example(s):</h3>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="px9rgs" data-video-descrip="In the &amp;quot;The Legend of Heroes&amp;quot; games, the characters use the ARCUS like a phone, and like a phone, nobody seems to say goodbye. In the case of Professor Schmidt from Cold Steel III (Sen No Kiseki III), he can't even be bothered to say &amp;quot;hello,&amp;quot; but then again, he has always been rather demanding." data-video-title="Demanding, As Always" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/px9rgs_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/px9rgs.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TVTelephoneEtiquette" data-video-tropename="TV Telephone Etiquette" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="1" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/TheLegendOfHeroesTrailsOfColdSteel" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
<div class="featured-widget-vid-iframe">
<video id='featured-video-player' class='video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-16-9' controls data-setup='{"ga": {"eventsToTrack": ["error"]}}'>
</video>
</div>
</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Demanding, As Always</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In the &quot;The Legend of Heroes&quot; games, the characters use the ARCUS like a phone, and like a phone, nobody seems to say goodbye. In the case of Professor Schmidt from Cold Steel III (Sen No Kiseki III), he can't even be bothered to say &quot;hello,&quot; but then again, he has always been rather demanding. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="ni983o" data-video-descrip="Peppa Pig hangs up on Suzy Sheep after she whistles, despite claiming not to know what whistling is." data-video-title="Peppa Pig Hangs Up" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/ni983o_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/ni983o.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TVTelephoneEtiquette" data-video-tropename="TV Telephone Etiquette" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/PeppaPig" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/ni983o.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Peppa Pig Hangs Up</span></p>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
